---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/ui/PageHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Bruce Denham | Adobe Award-Nominated Technical Writer & DX Engineer"
  description="Meet Bruce Denham: Adobe award-nominated Senior Technical Writer & Developer Experience Engineer with 30+ years transforming complex APIs into clear developer experiences at Adobe, TOPAZ, and Schlumberger."
  showBackLink={true}
  backLinkText="‚Üê Back to Home"
  backLinkHref="/"
  footerText="Want to collaborate? "
  footerLinkText="Let's connect on LinkedIn"
  footerLinkHref="https://linkedin.com/in/brucedenham/"
>
  <PageHeader primary="About" accent="Me" id="about-title" />

  <div class="intro-section">
    <div class="intro-content">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <p class="lead">
          üëã Hi there! I'm Bruce Denham, and I've spent 30+ years discovering that the secret to
          great documentation is becoming a member of your audience. When you become them, you
          experience all the pains and struggles they have. Then you can write your way out of it.
          That's the key. Turns out, most developers would rather write regex from scratch than read
          documentation‚Äîwhich is why I've made a career in making the inevitable less painful.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-image">
        <img
          src="/images/bruce-denham-og-card.jpg"
          alt="Bruce Denham - Adobe Award-Nominated Technical Writer & Developer Experience Engineer"
          width="300"
          height="157"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="recognition-section">
    <h2>Recognition & Community Impact</h2>
    <div class="recognition-grid">
      <div class="recognition-item">
        <h3>üèÜ Adobe Awards</h3>
        <p>
          Nominated for both the Adobe Founders Award and Extreme Ownership Award for excellence in
          technical writing and developer experience innovation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="recognition-item">
        <h3>üé§ International Speaking</h3>
        <p>
          Presented PageBuilder best practices at Meet Magento Indonesia 2019, sharing insights with
          the international open-source community.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="recognition-item">
        <h3>‚≠ê Community Leadership</h3>
        <p>
          PageBuilder Examples repository: 106 GitHub stars, 78 forks‚Äîhighest engagement in the
          PageBuilder ecosystem. Deep community involvement with Magento, contributing to both code
          and documentation that helps thousands of developers worldwide.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="recognition-item">
        <h3>üìö Mentoring & Education</h3>
        <p>
          Passionate about lifting others through shared knowledge, actively mentoring aspiring
          technical writers and students at Southwestern University. I also love to help teams
          establish effective documentation practices.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="journey-section">
    <h2>My Journey</h2>

    <div class="career-timeline">
      <div class="timeline-entry current">
        <div class="timeline-period">2018-now</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Adobe, Inc.</h3>
          <h4>Senior Technical Writer & Developer Experience Specialist</h4>
          <p>
            Leading documentation products across multiple teams at one of the world's premier
            creative software companies. I manage the Adobe Storefront Commerce documentation site,
            build interactive React apps for API demonstrations, and develop CLI tools that
            streamline developer workflows.
          </p>
          <p>
            My work includes everything from SDK documentation using Storybook 8 to custom Algolia
            search integrations that help developers find answers fast. I've been recognized by
            peers and leadership for creativity, UX expertise, and technical writing excellence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-entry">
        <div class="timeline-period">2006-2018</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>TOPAZ Technologies</h3>
          <h4>Senior Product Designer / Developer Support</h4>
          <p>
            During my 12 years at TOPAZ, I evolved from visual designer to full-stack product
            strategist. I led comprehensive UI overhauls of legacy AngularJS applications, trained
            development teams on Angular Material best practices, and managed end-to-end product
            marketing strategies.
          </p>
          <p>
            This role taught me the importance of bridging the gap between technical capability and
            user needs‚Äî a philosophy that continues to drive my approach to developer experience
            today.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-entry">
        <div class="timeline-period">2000-2005</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Schlumberger</h3>
          <h4>Senior Technical Writer / API Documentation Specialist</h4>
          <p>
            My foundation in technical writing was built in the oil & gas industry, where I wrote
            API documentation and training guides that enabled 100+ global developers to adopt
            complex systems quickly. I also built UI prototypes in C#/WinForms and integrated
            documentation directly into Microsoft Dev Studio.
          </p>
          <p>
            Working with engineers across different countries and cultures taught me that truly
            effective documentation transcends language barriers‚Äîit communicates through clarity,
            structure, and empathy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="expertise-section">
    <h2>What I Bring to the Table</h2>

    <div class="expertise-grid">
      <div class="expertise-category">
        <h3>Technical Writing & Documentation</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>API documentation that drives adoption</li>
          <li>Developer tutorials that simplify complex workflows</li>
          <li>Interactive playgrounds for hands-on learning</li>
          <li>Di√°taxis documentation framework expertise</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="expertise-category">
        <h3>Development & Tools</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>React 18+, Node.js, and modern JavaScript frameworks</li>
          <li>CLI tool development for productivity enhancement</li>
          <li>Git/GitHub workflows and automation</li>
          <li>Frontend development with responsive design</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="expertise-category">
        <h3>Visual Communication</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>UI/UX design for developer tools</li>
          <li>Infographics that clarify technical concepts</li>
          <li>Animation and video for process explanation</li>
          <li>Visual design that balances beauty and usability</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="expertise-category">
        <h3>Leadership & Strategy</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Cross-functional collaboration with UX, PM, and Engineering</li>
          <li>Developer advocacy and community building</li>
          <li>Remote team leadership and mentoring</li>
          <li>Product strategy aligned with user needs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="philosophy-section">
    <h2>My Philosophy</h2>
    <div class="philosophy-grid">
      <div class="philosophy-item">
        <div class="philosophy-icon">üéØ</div>
        <h3>I don't just write the docs</h3>
        <p>
          I build tools, craft interfaces, and create explanations that click. Understanding how
          things work from the inside makes all the difference in explaining them clearly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="philosophy-item">
        <div class="philosophy-icon">üí°</div>
        <h3>Spark "aha" moments</h3>
        <p>
          The best documentation doesn't just inform‚Äîit transforms confusion into confidence,
          complexity into clarity, and hesitation into action.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="philosophy-item">
        <div class="philosophy-icon">ü§ù</div>
        <h3>I code. I design. I connect.</h3>
        <p>
          Great developer experience happens at the intersection of technical accuracy, visual
          design, and human psychology. I work in all three spaces.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="philosophy-item">
        <div class="philosophy-icon">üöÄ</div>
        <h3>Reduce friction, increase flow</h3>
        <p>
          Every tool I build and every guide I write has one goal: help developers get from question
          to solution as smoothly as possible.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="personal-section">
    <h2>Beyond the Code</h2>
    <p>
      When I'm not crafting documentation or building developer tools, you'll find me exploring the
      latest in web technology, contributing to open-source projects, or mentoring aspiring
      technical writers. I'm energized by teaching and lifting others through shared knowledge.
    </p>
    <p>
      Based in the Austin, Texas metropolitan area, I thrive in remote team environments and have
      been successfully working remotely for 5+ years. I believe the best developer experiences are
      built through diverse, distributed teams that bring different perspectives to solving complex
      problems.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-section">
    <h2>Let's Build Better Developer Experiences Together</h2>
    <p>
      Whether you're looking to improve your documentation, build better developer tools, or create
      clearer technical communication, I'd love to hear about your challenges and explore how we
      might work together.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* About page styles */
  .intro-section {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .intro-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .intro-image {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .intro-image img {
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--shadow-secondary);
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .intro-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .intro-text {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .intro-image img {
      width: 280px;
      height: auto;
    }
  }

  .journey-section,
  .philosophy-section,
  .expertise-section,
  .recognition-section,
  .personal-section,
  .cta-section {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .journey-section h2,
  .philosophy-section h2,
  .expertise-section h2,
  .recognition-section h2,
  .personal-section h2,
  .cta-section h2 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-primary);
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .career-timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 32px;
  }

  .career-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 16px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--border-primary);
  }

  .timeline-entry {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card), rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.02));
    border: 2px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin-left: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-entry.current {
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card), rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.02));
  }

  .timeline-entry:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--shadow-secondary);
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  /* .timeline-entry::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -24px;
    top: 24px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    background: var(--accent-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
  } */

  .timeline-entry.current::before {
    background: var(--accent-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.2);
  }

  .timeline-period {
    position: absolute;
    left: -80px;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    color: var(--accent-yellow);
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-yellow);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    font-size: 22px;
  }

  .timeline-content h4 {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .timeline-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .philosophy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .philosophy-item {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card), rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.02));
    border: 2px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .philosophy-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--shadow-secondary);
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .philosophy-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }

  .philosophy-item h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .philosophy-item p {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .expertise-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .expertise-category {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card), rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.02));
    border: 2px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .expertise-category:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--shadow-secondary);
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .expertise-category h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .expertise-category ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .expertise-category li {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding-left: 16px;
    position: relative;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .expertise-category li::before {
    content: '‚ñ∏';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .recognition-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }

  /* Match standard 2-card responsive behavior */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .recognition-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .recognition-item {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card), rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.02));
    border: 2px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    /* Page load animation */
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    animation: slideInUp 400ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) forwards;
  }

  .recognition-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--shadow-secondary);
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .recognition-item h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .recognition-item p {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Staggered animation delays */
  .recognition-item:nth-child(1) {
    animation-delay: 100ms;
  }

  .recognition-item:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 200ms;
  }

  .recognition-item:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 300ms;
  }

  .recognition-item:nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: 400ms;
  }

  .personal-section p,
  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .personal-section p:last-child,
  .cta-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .career-timeline {
      padding-left: 16px;
    }

    .timeline-entry {
      margin-left: 8px;
    }

    .timeline-period {
      left: -100px;
      font-size: 10px;
      padding: 2px 4px;
    }

    .philosophy-grid,
    .expertise-grid,
    .recognition-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
